text: == Events == * Liudolf, Duke of Swabia and Conrad the Red rebel against German King Otto I. == Births == * Charles, Duke of Lower Lorraine * Herbert III, Count of Vermandois * Al-Karaji, Persian mathematician and engineer * Kisai Marvazi, Persian poet == Deaths == * Abas I of Armenia, King of Armenia * Ismail al-Mansur. third Fatimid Caliph * Empress Dowager Yingtian of the Liao Dynasty * Muhammad bin Musafir, Sallarid ruler of Tarum and Iranian Azerbaijan * Rasso, Bavarian count, military leader, pilgrim, and saint. * Rhodri ap Hywel, king of Deheubarth
